snippet.title: Cute FUNNY PUPPIES are the BEST ANIMALS - LAUGH NOW!
snippet.description:
Puppies are so sweet, cute and funny animals! Puppies make us laugh all the time and are the best entertainment in the World! This super cute and funny puppy compilation is the hardest try not to laugh challenge ever! Look how all these puppies fail, make funny sounds, play, sleep,... So super funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
